Charles Wang - Wikipedia





















 






Charles Wang

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Charles B. Wang)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

This article is about the businessman. For other uses, see Charles Wang (disambiguation).





This article has an unclear citation style. The references used may be made clearer with a different or consistent style of citation, footnoting, or external linking. (July 2013) (Learn how and when to remove this template message)




Charles Wang
王嘉廉


Born
(1944-08-19) August 19, 1944 (age 72)
Shanghai, Republic of China


Occupation



Owner, New York Islanders
